name: Wesa Ready To Do Our-sa Part (V)
Lore: 'Every Gungan that died on the battle plains gave Amidala and her troops that much more time to capture the Viceroy.',
Text: 'Deploy on Endor system or Naboo system. Your total power here is +1 for each Ewok or Gungan at related sites. Once per turn, may place your just lost Ewok or Gungan in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
